# Design System — Trika Yoga & Wellness

## Feel Like

Luxury wellness retreat · contemporary art gallery · premium editorial magazine · Aman Resorts · Apple product launch · high-end architecture studio.

**Not:** yoga website · wellness coach template · WordPress theme · Webflow clone.

## Colors

| Token | Hex |
|-------|-----|
| Primary (Terracotta) | `#A55A42` |
| Secondary (Sand) | `#D8C5A4` |
| Accent (Sage) | `#7A8B6F` |
| Text (Charcoal) | `#2B2B2B` |
| Background (Bone) | `#F8F5F0` |
| Corporate Dark | `#1A1A1A` |

## Typography

- **Headings:** Cormorant Garamond — huge, layered, editorial
- **Body:** Inter — restrained, never walls of text
- **Buttons:** Inter SemiBold

## Layout Principles

- Asymmetrical compositions — avoid centered-everything
- Generous whitespace — reveal content progressively, not all at once
- Section padding: 120px / 80px / 60px (desktop/tablet/mobile)
- Mix: full-width imagery · editorial · split-screen · horizontal scroll

## Animation

0.8–1.2s · `ease-out` · fade, blur reveal, parallax, soft scale. Never bounce or slider carousels.

Inspiration: Aman · Apple · Linear · Arc · Kinfolk · Aesop

